+        Data generation only requires the model *metadata* (e.g. to build the
+        frequency domain and injection settings), not the full network. dingo_pipe
+        extracts the metadata from the model and stores it in the complete config file
+        as ``model_metadata``, which avoids transferring the large network to the
+        generation node. If the metadata is unavailable (e.g. when running generation
+        directly without dingo_pipe), fall back to loading it from the model file.
